                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-71-off379 t18020918-71-cd380"></join>, fifty-five yards of dimity, value 5l. the property of<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="180209180043"></xptr>
                  
                     
