                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-71-defend544 t18020918-71-punish383"></join>
               Death
            </rs>, aged 20.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Le Blanc.</p>
